title: #33 Danny Recaps Iconic Reality TV With Ben & Ronnie from Watch What Crappens, Chats With Kelly Killoren Bensimon & Jules Wainstein (Formerly of #RHONY), Plus Courtney Frain From Two Judgey Girls

description:
Ben Mandelker & Ronnie Karam from the Watch What Crappens podcast are here to talk to Danny about the #RHOA reunion, the #RHONY premiere, Southern Charm, & more. Plus, Danny chats w/ two of the stars of two of the most iconic reality TV seasons of all time- Kelly Killoren Bensimon & Jules Wainstein of #RHONY. Courtney Frain of @TwoJudgeyGirls also pops by to do a reality TV lightning round. 

*For bonus Everything Iconic, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com
